	\t8.  View all the current running process
	\t9.  Create user by entering unique username and password
	\t10. Delete existing user
	\t11. File handling(.txt file)
	\t12. EXIT\nEnter your choice : """, end = "")
	if(in1 == 1):
		system("espeak-ng  \"heyy hi\"")
